             was indicted for <rs id="t17930529-8-off37" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930529-8-off37" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930529-8-off37" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17930529-8-cd38" type="crimeDate">6th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930529-8-off37 t17930529-8-cd38"></join>, 13 l. in monies numbered; the monies of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17930529-8-victim144" type="victimName">
